<br>
Next got a SK Troll cause I liked the look..They are rather hard to level and I couldn't cast my pet right away cause he was so stupid, made a Troll warrior instead..leveled hard.<br>
<br>
Ended up playing a wood elf druid because traveling around on the boats, across the Karanas, etc was for the birds. Got him up to level 22, stopped playing EQ and let a friend use the account, he got him back to 35, where I played again and then left for DAOC, and now he's level 42 =) <br>
<br>
I now am playing a Eurodite Pally cause well a friend of mine just happened to have enough gear to last me into my 40's laying around..It's fun again and I'm now up to 25 =)  So theres my story =)  <p>"In theory, there is no difference between theory
